  "description": "<p><u><strong>URGENT!🥤PART TIME DRINK KIOSK ASSISTANTS| $12/HR PAID BI-WEEKLY)</strong></u><br /><br />📍Location: Chinatown/Ang Mo Kio/Pasir Ris </p><p>💰Salary: $12/hr  </p><p>Public holidays double pay!  </p><p>🗓️Working days: 5 day work week (Between Mon-Sun) </p><p>🕑Shift hours: 9am-3pm / 11am-5pm / 4.30pm-10.30pm  </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Make and serve different kinds of tea drinks, including special requests from customers. </p></li><li><p>Help with testing, preparing, and packing food and snacks. </p></li><li><p>Keep the work area clean and follow food safety and hygiene rules. </p></li><li><p>Use tea-making machines and handle customer orders and cash properly and quickly </p></li></ul><p>Requirements: </p><ul><li><p>WSQ Food and Hygiene Level 1 Certificate </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
